good gorgeous colour exactly what i wanted beautifully made and packed arrived before scheduled time loved them i brought it for just rs 1495 during the offer usually it costs around 2495 its worth buying it very comfortable to wearfully satisfied instead of buying new footwears every monthbuy this once and it will last till 3 4 yrs buy it order one size smaller than normal if you generally order uk8 order us8uk7 here this was a bit too big great comfort and amazing durability worth the money it is good quality product worthy nice one the comfort is on next level and i have never felt this comfort in any other clogs that i have worn so far i got it for 1200 during festive sale

always buy crocs from cocoblu retail only as they provide genuine crocs product which i have observed so far
i had ordered the same pair on flipkart and got a fake one

the stucco color is same like the yeezy foam runner bone color
overall the most satisfying purchase so far go for it blindly even if you get it for 1400 or 1500 nice
